# Site shell (1920px max)

All page content is capped at **1920px** (`--site-max-width`), centered on the viewport.

- `html` background: **#FCF9F9** — visible in side gutters when viewport > 1920px
- `body` + fixed `.nav-wrapper`: `max-width: 1920px`, centered

Full-width sections (`layout--full`) still span 100% of the **body** column (up to 1920px), not the full monitor beyond that.
